nal Decision:**\n    *   Output: 你好！有什么我可以帮你的吗？"},{"role":"user","content":"你好","createdAt":"2026-04-20T10:19:04.224Z"},{"role":"assistant","content":"你好！有什么我可以帮你的吗？","reasoningContent":"Thinking Process:\n\n1.  **Analyze the Input:**\n    *   Input: \"你好\" (Nǐ hǎo)\n    *   Language: Chinese (Simplified)\n    *   Meaning: \"Hello\" / \"Hi\"\n    *   Intent: Greeting / Starting a conversation.\n\n2.  **Determine the Appropriate Response:**\n    *   Tone: Friendly, polite, helpful.\n    *   Language: Chinese (Simplified) to match the user.\n    *   Content: Acknowledge the greeting, offer assistance.\n\n3.  **Drafting Responses:**\n    *   Option 1 (Simple): 你好！有什么我可以帮你的吗？ (Hello! Is there anything I can help you with?)\n    *   Option 2 (Friendly): 你好呀！今天过得怎么样？ (Hello there! How''s your day going?)\n    *   Option 3 (Professional): 您好，我是人工智能助手。请问有什么需要？ (Hello, I am an AI assistant. What do you need?)\n    *   Option 4 (Balanced): 你好！很高兴见到你。有什么我可以帮你的吗？ (Hello! Nice to meet you. Is there anything I can help you with?)\n\n4.  **Selecting the Best Response:**\n    *   Option 4 is a good balance of friendly and helpful.\n    *   Keep it concise but open-ended.\n\n5.  **Final Polish (in Chinese):**\n    *   \"你好！很高兴为你服务。有什么我可以帮你的吗？\" (Hello! Glad to serve you. Is there anything I can help you with?)\n    *   Or simply: \"你好！有什么我可以帮你的吗？\" (Hello! Is there anything I can help you with?)\n\n6.  **Final Decision:**\n    *   \"你好！有什么我可以帮你的吗？\" (Standard, polite, helpful)\n    *   Add a bit of warmth: \"你好呀！有什么我可以帮你的吗？\" (Slightly more casual/friendly)\n    *   Let''s go with a standard friendly greeting.\n\n    *Selected:* 你好！有什么我可以帮你的吗？ (Hello! Is there anything I can help you with?)\n\n7.  **Output Generation:** (Translate thought to output)\n    你好！有什么我可以帮你的吗？","createdAt":"2026-04-20T10:19:04.224Z"},{"role":"user","content":"你好啊","createdAt":"2026-04-20T10:32:36.087Z"},{"role":"assistant","content":"你好啊！👋 今天过得怎么样？有什么想聊的或者需要帮忙的吗？","createdAt":"2026-04-20T10:32:36.087Z"},{"r